      "message": "I agree that this path is kind of strange since it has both \u0027power_supplies\u0027 and \u0027psus\u0027 in it.\n\nHowever, this is used in several other places, such as:\n* https://github.com/openbmc/phosphor-power/blob/master/types.hpp#L48\n* https://github.com/openbmc/phosphor-state-manager/blob/master/chassis_state_manager.cpp#L87\n\nThis path is how the PSU app communicates that a brownout is occurring to other applications.\n\nSo you need to either leave it the same or change those other places too.",
